revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yeatmans}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yeatman'' is the 26549<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 918 individuals. ''Yeatman'' is most common among White (93.36%) individuals.
